### 모든 제품 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/products

### 제품 생성 (판매용)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "캠핑 텐트",
  "stockQuantity": 10,
  "price": 150000,
  "productType": "SALE"
}

### 제품 생성 (렌탈용)
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "캠핑 의자",
  "stockQuantity": 20,
  "price": 5000,
  "productType": "RENTAL"
}

### 제품 수정
PUT http://localhost:8080/admin/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "수정된 제품명",
  "stockQuantity": 15,
  "price": 200000,
  "productType": "SALE"
}